welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Delaware, the charming state with picturesque beaches and historical landmarks. Get ready to explore its beauty and immerse yourself in its rich culture. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Ohio State University Airport serves commercial flights and offers a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Ohio State University Airport caters to private and charter flights, providing a luxurious and exclusive experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Complimentary wifi is available throughout the airport for all passengers.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Municipal Airport houses all major airlines and provides a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Regional Terminal
terminals.description: The regional terminal at Municipal Airport serves smaller airlines and offers a more intimate and convenient travel experience.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.name: Concourse A
